finalproject.objects

Class GameData

  • java.lang.Object
    • finalproject.objects.GameData

  • public class GameData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class hold all values that are transmitted to the robot over Wi-Fi at the beginning of the game. This class provides functionality to transform a Map object coming from the WifiConnection class and assign the values to local class variables.
    Author:
    maxsn
